Michael Ban was a great friend to my brother Joey.  He was an athlete, accomplished lawyer, devoted husband, son and brother.  He is a Pittsburgh Legend for his warrior strength and awesome sense of humor while gallantly facing a terminal illness. 

In his thirties, Ban was diagnosed with brain cancer but he never let the prognosis kill his spirit.  He would arrive to the hospital smiling in a three-piece suit for each of his dozen brain surgeries, excited to see his doctors and nurses. He lived the words: “Fate whispers to the warrior ‘you cannot withstand the storm.’ the warrior whispers back ‘ I am the storm’.” 

Before his last surgery, while his body was getting weaker, he made sure to deliver personal tokens of his love to those close to him. Ban gave my brother Joey his sports jacket. On May 24, 2022 Michael Ban crossed the bridge to Heaven.  Joey wears Ban’s jacket on holidays and shares stories to keep his memory alive.  This week Ban showed that he continues to write his own story and inspire from the skies. #pittsburgh

Recording an album of original songs with Khari Mateen as executive producer in Brenham, Texas at his magical studio THE SIDE DOOR 🎶✨

When @diceraw first brought me in Larry Gold’s “The Studio” when I was 19 to do a writing session and meet Richard Nichols, manager of @theroots , I never thought that I’d get to work with musicians who produced for Legendary artists such as The Roots, Jill Scott and Jazmine Sullivan who inspired me over the years. 

@kharrari , @stevemckiebeats and @anthonycraigbell are producing tracks. Can’t wait for you to hear what we’re creating! 

#brenham #brenhamtx #texas #singersongwriter #recording #philly #pitupatter #monheimmics

Elle.Morris and I met 10 years ago in Philly at “The Studio” - 413 North 7th street, when we started performing together with the talented Ashley Howard @iamprettygirl85 , CJ Branch @cj_branch, Harry Wilson @harrywilson6str , Andre Pinckney @drepinckney , Jon Smith @jonsmith5string and Anwar Marshall @anwarmarshall. Since then @i.love.elle.morris has gone on to musical direct, songwrite, vocal arrange and has her solo artist debut February 2024 🩷

After finishing lead vocals to 8 original songs for my album, executive produced by film composer & producer Khari Mateen @kharrari , excited to have Elle executive produce the background vocals. We got a couple surprises with legendary recording artists features before we deliver the tracks to be mixed by Grammy nominated, multi-platinum Calin Enache @districtsoundlab. Stay tuned 🫶
#pitupatter #singersongwriter #recording #philly #texas

Working on “Pitupatter” album 💿 with Executive Producer Khari Mateen at his studio “Side Door”🫶 

@kharrari is a prolific film composer too! To name a few of his many works, he scored the music for “Really Love” on @netflix and co-composed the score for Murdaugh Murders documentary.
